    <record id="set_cocktail_party" model="lcs.catering.set">
        <field name="name">Corporate Cocktail Party 公司雞尾酒會</field>
        <field name="product_id" ref="product_cocktail_party"/>
        <field name="recommendation">Executive Cocktail Package — for 50+ guests.
Choose ONE package tier first (6/8/10/12 canapes per person), then pick canapes from the 5 sections.
Total picks must match the chosen tier. Items marked +HK$10/+HK$20 add to the per-person price.
Standard drinks included. Deluxe drink upgrade adds wine &amp; beer (+HK$60/person).
Includes 3 waiters (4 hrs), tablecloth, glassware, paper napkins, reusable tableware, food labels, delivery.
Pass-around service may need extra waitstaff (contact CS).</field>
    </record>

